{
  "stem": "17135.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a very strong door to the entrance to the apartments.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they scream all the time, are there Jews, more Jews, in that house?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they did in many instances, they beat up people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were drunk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the police did not interfere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The police had strict-- we found out after, two days later-- everybody, every Jew had one friend at the police.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they mostly informed of what was going on, even among the gestapo, interesting enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were Germans that somehow knew some of the Jewish citizens for years and years, at least informed him, watch it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is an action being planned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hide, don't be at home, what have you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Interesting enough, there were actions by the Nazis, by the Gestapo, when you were not at home, you were-- you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I give an example.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you remember-- let me tell you a story about the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were knocking at the door and wanted to get up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And fortunately enough, on the top floor, there was a very poor German family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother was very philanthropic, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Poor people, if they were Jewish, or Germans, she helped him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "From the store, stuff that didn't sell, she'd give to-- [INAUDIBLE] she had six children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And one of her sons, I think it was the oldest son, became an SS man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "SS man.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and he did not make nasty remarks to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because his mother didn't tolerate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we begged the mother, please, tell your son to go to the window and tell the-- the people downstairs there are no Jews here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And let him put on his SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She didn't want to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my mother begged her and cried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Eventually, he did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
